rows.label: qst104213_msg0001
rows.name:
Legendary hero...mo... sparkly
princess...mo... tiny fairy...mo...

rows.label: qst104213_msg0002
rows.name:
Mo-mo! Lapupu was lost in
the world of a book, mo.

rows.label: qst104213_msg0003
rows.name:
Lapupu is still just a child, and
not a sparkly princess, but...mo.

rows.label: qst104213_msg0004
rows.name:
Inside a book, Lapupu can be a hero,
a princess, or even a fairy, mo!

rows.label: qst104213_msg0005
rows.name:
If you become someone wonderful, you can
understand others and become kinder...
Lapupu wants to teach everyone that, mo.

rows.label: qst104213_msg0006
rows.name:
Lapupu as a teacher in Iyasaki
Village? What to do...mo...

rows.label: qst104213_msg0007
rows.name:
Mom always say Nopon should follow
heart and live free, so she probably
not object, but still...

rows.label: qst104213_msg0008
rows.name:
You see, Mama always tells
me I'm too young and don't
need them, but...mo...

rows.label: qst104213_msg0009
rows.name:
Lapupu wants to buy
cosmetics and accessories
to become a princess, mo.

rows.label: qst104213_msg0010
rows.name:
Lapupu wants to try being a princess
outside of a book, too, mo.

rows.label: qst104213_msg0011
rows.name:
Lapupu wants 7,500G for
a shopping spree, mo.

rows.label: qst104213_msg0012
rows.name: Pay 7,500G?

rows.label: qst104213_msg0013
rows.name: Pay

rows.label: qst104213_msg0014
rows.name: Don't pay

rows.label: qst104213_msg0081
rows.name:
Too bad, mo... When Lapupu
gets bigger, Lapupu will
buy them herself, mo.

rows.label: qst104213_msg0082
rows.name:
By then, maybe Lapupu will already
be a sparkly princess...mo?

rows.label: qst104213_msg0101
rows.name:
With 7,500G, Lapupu can go
on a shopping spree and
become a princess...mo...

rows.label: qst104213_msg0151
rows.name:
Yay, yay! Time to shop, mo~!
Time to become a princess, mo~!

rows.label: qst104213_msg0152
rows.name:
After Lapupu is done being
a princess, Lapupu will go
to Iyasaki Village, mo.

rows.label: qst104213_msg0153
rows.name:
This is Lapupu's first time on an
adventure outside of a book, mo!

rows.label: qst104213_msg0154
rows.name: See you later, mo~!

rows.label: qst104213_msg0181
rows.name:
Have you decided on a teacher,
mo? Lapupu tried being a teacher
in a book. It was fun, mo.

rows.label: qst104213_msg0201
rows.name:
Someday, Lapupu wants to
become a princess outside
of a book, too, mo~.
